---
title: North African-Style Loaded Beef Bowls with Roasted Sweet Potatoes
description: Get ready for explosions of flavour and colour with this hearty veggie and beef salad! Moroccan-spiced roasted sweet potatoes and harissa onions bring depth and warmth to this weeknight wonder.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-boeuf-garnis-a-la-nord-africaine-c13d521e.jpg
